stories.text: I frequently think about doing writing an app or web service, but then talk myself out of it by thinking that the effort is much greater than it sounds and those efforts would be better off trying to progress my career. Is anyone here actually enjoying a few hundred dollars a month from an app or web-service that was worth it after your initial effort and ongoing maintenance?
